4. Update 4 route templates to render `<LensPanel />` before `<Content />`
5. Add inline lens panels to 5 section index pages via imported LensPanel with inline data

**Discriminator result**: PA5 (Hybrid) scored 24/25 — highest across empirical (5), parsimony (5), consensus (5), chain integrity (5), predictive power (4). Full analysis: `content/analysis/lens-copy-implementation-discriminator.md`

**Content calibration by persona**:
- **Voter** (Grade 8): Personal impact framing, household-level language, action link
