- #AI 788, #GenerativeAI 90, #ArtificialIntelligence 85, #opensource 157, #cybersecurity 290
- #humanrights 41, #HRC61 (active event), #democracy 33, #LGBTQ 344, #MutualAid 263

**Files modified**: `plan.md.marketing` — "Bluesky Hashtag Intelligence" section appended

**What follows**: Campaign posts 3-18 use the recommended combinations from plan.md.marketing. #HRC61 posts should go before March 31. ISHR and HRW follow-back list in marketing notes.

